Switzerland was absolutely stunning! All five senses were stimulated in the best way possible. Pictures truly do no justice. From the rolling green hills spotted with yellow dandelions and flowers, to the snowcapped mountains peaking through the clouds, smelling and tasting the fresh Gruyère cheese, straight from the source, the delicious cherry tomatoes, bursting with juice, you could taste the earth and all the flavors she had to offer, inhaling the fresh mountain air, hearing the cow bells of the roaming cattle and endless chirping of the birds singing their songs, ending with the epic tour on the Glacier Express winding through the Alps. Everywhere I turned, it was like a picturesque postcard. I’ll never forget my time here🇨🇭 

#switzerland #geneva #gruyere #stmoritz #zurmatt #travel #europe #mountains #alps #glacierexpress #trains #nature #beauty
Germany 🇩🇪

More Germany (Munich & Berlin) highlights! One of my favorite memories of the country will be the Ludwig castle tour just outside of Munich, where we took a horse drawn carriage up through the misty forest, then hiked up a bit to reach the bridge for a stunning view of Neuschwanstein Castle. Definitely worth the trek in the rain to get the photo. A very magical place indeed. Loved the old and new architecture in Berlin and learning the history behind the rebuilding of the city. And yes, German beer is delicious! 

#travel #germany #munich #berlin #castles #architecture #love #instagood#photooftheday #beautiful #art #happy #nature #europe
